<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Notice of Platform Membership Restriction and Resolution Process</title>
</head>
<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
    }
    h3 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    h4 {
        font-size: 19px;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    p {
        font-size: 18px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
</style>
<body>
    <h3>Dear <%= memberName %>,</h3>
    <p>We trust this message finds you well.</p>
    <p>We regret to inform you that, due to recent activity on our platform, your access has been temporarily restricted. Upon review, it was determined that there were violations of our platform guidelines, prompting this action.</p>
    <p>Your account will remain restricted until <b><%= duration %></b>. However, we understand the importance of resolving this matter swiftly. To initiate the resolution process and uplift the restriction, we kindly request that you reach out to this email. We will provide guidance and assistance in understanding the circumstances surrounding the restriction and working towards a resolution.</p>
    <p>Your understanding and cooperation in adhering to our platform guidelines are greatly appreciated as we strive to maintain a safe and conducive environment for all members.</p>
    <p>Thank you for your attention to this matter.</p>
    <p>Sincerely,</p>
    <h4>The BiCoRSE Management</h4>
</body>
</html>
